{"tid":1459191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊要］以後開始搭港鐵要跳閘，直到五大訴求得到回應！","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:38:42.000Z","uid":201581,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8901e62f3a7a8b63d28c57b2148f226b756abf9f","tid":1459191,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:27:44.000Z","msg":"其實我地捉住政府個春袋已經好大優勢！但係我地要識得善用！<br />\n就係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長期癱瘓機場！係長期！</span><br />\n長期既意思唔係要佔領！係每日癱瘓，唔洗過夜留守<br />\n第二：<br />\n以後搭港鐵唔好再拍卡比鐵！全民跳入閘！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直至五大訴求得到正面回應</span></span><br />\n我地無謂再搞塞地鐵！塞地鐵某程度影響民生！<br />\n我地要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利用</span></span>地鐵，減少狗鐵收入之餘！仲可以減少政府其中一個收入！<br />\n要全民免費搭地鐵！贏民心，得天下！<br />\n<br />\n記住:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跳閘！跳閘！跳閘</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"c2c4233546e1c8ca97cb91a4fff247d36da66c5f","tid":1459191,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:28:04.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835dc80b4317b0ed5f32a2b001352da5d3bf76aa","tid":1459191,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"緊要野自推十下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a27d010ea47a80389c0ce1fd933522fe304828","tid":1459191,"uid":251167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"721 <br />\n811"},{"pid":"07bf4c1c1b45cb0a9f94472cb55fb2723ea9041a","tid":1459191,"uid":180786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:29:37.00